data.description: Welcome to this spacious ranch nestled on a .3 acre corner lot in picturesque Sullivan, Missouri. Completely remodeled in 2018, this 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom house boasts the perfect combination of modern and cozy throughout the main floor. The fenced-in backyard features a brand-new deck and plenty of space for everyone to spread out and enjoy different activities. The partially finished, walk-out basement provides plenty of storage and a huge bonus/bedroom with an egress window.  Schedule an appointment to view this stunning listing, and take steps towards making this house YOUR home before it is too late.
